SvcWatchDog is based on PJ Naughter's CNTService class, which is a wrapper
around the Windows Service API. You can find more information about it here:
http://www.naughter.com/serv.html
Fragments of CNTService code were used with explicit permission by the
author. Thanks to PJ Naughter ( http://www.naughter.com/ ) for his work and
for allowing us to use it!


